These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-1::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: rose, sunflower, poppy
1. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
2. the person who growspoppy is between the person who growsrose and the person who growssunflower##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2   |    3     |
| Flower   | rose | poppy | sunflower |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, lemonade, tea
1. the person drinking 7up is between the person drinking lemonade and the person drinking tea##2
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | tea | 7up | lemonade |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-3::.
City: paris, liverpool, berlin
1. the person traveling to liverpool is between the person traveling to paris and the person traveling to berlin##2
2. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |  2   |    3    |
| City   | berlin | liverpool | paris |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-4::.
