.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-5::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, november, june
1. the person who's birthday is in april is between the person who's birthday is in june and the person who's birthday is in november##2
2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |  2   |  3   |
| Birthday   | november | april | june |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-6::.
